# BeActive - Swedish Activity Booking Platform

This is a modern Swedish activity booking platform built with Next.js 16, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui components.

## Key Technologies
- **Next.js 16** with App Router
- **TypeScript** for type safety
- **Tailwind CSS** for styling
- **shadcn/ui** for UI components
- **Mapbox GL JS** for interactive maps
- **Swiper** for carousels
- **Unsplash API** for images
- **Lucide React** for icons

## Project Structure
- [src/app/](mdc:src/app/) - Next.js app router pages
- [src/components/](mdc:src/components/) - React components
- [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui/) - shadcn/ui components
- [src/lib/](mdc:src/lib/) - Utilities, types, and data
- [src/hooks/](mdc:src/hooks/) - Custom React hooks

## Key Files
- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with Swedish localization
- [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Home page with map and carousels
- [src/lib/types.ts](mdc:src/lib/types.ts) - TypeScript interfaces
- [src/lib/mock-data.ts](mdc:src/lib/mock-data.ts) - Mock activity data
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - shadcn/ui configuration

## Environment Variables Required
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_ACCESS_TOKEN` - For map functionality
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY` - For fetching images